==Winners==
The winners were announced on April 20 2026<ref>[https://ask.vrchat.com/t/space-jam-3-world-film-winners/48309 'Space Jam 3: World & Film Winners'] posted via ''ask.vrchat.com'' on April 20, 2026; retrieved April 20, 2026</ref>, there are a total of 8 world winners and 13 film winners.

World winners are showcased in the "Space Jam 3" world row which went live on April 20th and ends on May 31st. While the Film winners are showcased on the VRChat YouTube channel, and a screening of the winning films will be hosted on May 1st by the Filmmakers of VRChat group.

