== Collaborations ==
=== Strange Pear Gallery of Fine Arts ===
On April 8, 2026, VRChat announced a collaboration between the [[Special:MyLanguage/Community:Strange Pear Gallery of Fine Arts|Strange Pear Gallery of Fine Arts]] and Space Jam.<ref>[https://bsky.app/profile/vrchat.com/post/3miyuvcb5f22n VRChat announcement] on ''Bluesky''. Dated April 8, 2026. Retrieved April 8, 2026.</ref> The contest invites fine art submissions through the Strange Pear Discord, with selected works to be featured in a digital fine arts gallery hosted in VRChat. Submissions are open until May 1, 2026.

